    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Anchietea ferrucciae Paula-Souza & Zmarzty, sp. nov. A. habit, B. calyx, C. corolla, D. ovary and pedicel, E. anterior stamen, F. posterior stamen, G. seed. (A based on Stannard H51721 (SPF); B–F based on Souza & Sakuragui 50259 (SPF); G based on Paula-Souza et al. 5349 (SPF). Drawn by Klei Sousa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10084129/files/figure.png" ;
