<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10084134>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Seeds of extra-Andean species of Anchietea (from dried herbarium specimens). A. Anchietea ferrucciae (Paula-Souza et al. 5349), B. A. selloviana (Stehmann & Mendonça s.n. BHCB 20311), C. A. exalata (Paula-Souza & Leite 9596), D. A. pyrifolia (Paula-Souza et al. 8735). Photos: J.Paula-Souza." ;
